data.description: Welcome to this well-cared-for home in the exclusive Shenandoah gated community. This large, corner lot sits at the heart of the neighborhood, easily walkable to the community pool, tennis courts and playground. The beautifully landscaped yard invites you in with it's mature trees and sprawling flower beds. The open floorplan flows from the grand foyer, through the large formal living and dining rooms and into the upgraded kitchen which boasts stainless steel appliances. The kitchen opens to a sun drenched nook with a picturesque view of the backyard. The family room makes a statement with its upgraded stone fireplace and beautiful hardwood floors. The main floor also features a cozy office/study just off the formal dining room. Head upstairs for 4 of the 5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, including an expansive primary suite with a 5 piece bathroom and closets galore. Head to the basement for the 5th bedroom with a walk in closet and a bonus room to make your own. Enjoy the private backyard with an expansive composite deck and salt-water hot tub. To top it off, Nine Mile Light Rail Station, access to I-225 and Cherry Creek State Park are minutes away. Come see this stunning property in person!
